.DT 
set_level 
Discworld monster help 
set_level 

Name
.SI 5
set_level - Sets the level of the monster.
.EI

Syntax
.SI 5
void set_level(int lvl);
.EI

Description
.SP 5 5
This sets the default experience of the monster up and also calls
functions on both the race and guild objects to set up the race and
guild specific details.  This should give a rough estimation of how good
the monster is.
.EP

See also
.SP 5 5
query_level, set_race, set_guild
.EP
